2.1.2 Installing the carousel cover and platform

Prior to performing any work on electrical components, unplug the instrument from mains.

1. Install transformer shield (23) and connect grounding cable (PE) - see chapter 3.9.4.

2. Screw cable clip (22) nut (20) and washer (21) on transformer shield (23).

3. Fasten transformer shield (23) with screws (15) and washers (16).

4. Close front cover (19) and secure with screw (17) and washer (18).

5. Position platform (14) in place, fasten screws (12) together with washers (13).

6. Tighten screws (11) and insert retaining device G (9) and retaining device P (10).

7. Position casing (8) and lid (7) in place and fasten circlip (6).

8. Position carrier plate (5) in place.

9. Adjust carrier plate (5) - see chapter 2.2.1.

10.Put on carousel cover (1) and rotate clockwise once to fasten.

