7.3 Adjusting the lid weight

There are two cable links on the electronics board which permit adjusting the drive to the weight of the rotor. The rotor weight differs in the different TP 1020 models. Standard configuration is the one in model C (in bold letters), i.e. this type of control electronics has to be kept in stock by electronics manufacturing by all means.

