18.2 Reagents appropriate for use with the instrument

Using other than the reagents listed below can cause damage to the instrument or to parts of the instrument.

The following reagents are safe for use with the TP1020:

Fixation Formalin, buffered or unbuffered Picric acid

Dehydration Ethanol Isopropyl alcohol Methanol Butyl alcohol Industrial alcohol

